6. Main transactional load (Sequence Container)
Add Sequence Container: SEQ_Load_CES_From_IFS.

TransactionOption = Required.

Connect SQL_Get_CESConn → SEQ_Load_CES_From_IFS.

Inside SEQ_Load_CES_From_IFS:

